    },
    {
      "start": 10.23,
      "end": 30.27,
      "text": "영어와 영화 감상을 동시에"
    },
    {
      "start": 30.27,
      "end": 32.65,
      "text": "Killing two birds with one stone."
    },
    {
      "start": 32.87,
      "end": 34.25,
      "text": "Screen English time!"
    },
    {
      "start": 34.98,
      "end": 37.82,
      "text": "3월에 함께하고 있는 영화는 어디갔어, 버나데드?"
    },
    {
      "start": 38.2,
      "end": 39.24,
      "text": "Where'd you go, 버나데드?"
    },
    {
      "start": 39.24,
      "end": 42.08,
      "text": "Directed by Richard Linklater."
    },
    {
      "start": 42.26,
      "end": 44.98,
      "text": "네, 너무 귀여운 소리를 내주신 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 45.26,
      "end": 45.46,
      "text": "아."
    },
    {
      "start": 45.72,
      "end": 46.86,
      "text": "강아지인 줄 알았어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 47.06,
      "end": 49.12,
      "text": "It was a little salt and pepper."
    },
    {
      "start": 49.5,
      "end": 49.88,
      "text": "네, 네."
    },
    {
      "start": 49.88,
      "end": 50.94,
      "text": "A little 양념."
    },
    {
      "start": 51.06,
      "end": 52.38,
      "text": "아, 너무 즐겁습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 52.76,
      "end": 56.14,
      "text": "어머, 백준현님께서 질문을 하나 해주셨는데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 56.28,
      "end": 56.58,
      "text": "Please."
    },
    {
      "start": 56.84,
      "end": 59.04,
      "text": "여섯시 내고양에 나온 크리스님 맞나요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 59.28,
      "end": 60.12,
      "text": "여섯시 내고양이요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 60.2,
      "end": 60.5,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 60.64,
      "end": 61.3,
      "text": "여섯시 내고양?"
    },
    {
      "start": 61.42,
      "end": 61.64,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 61.88,
      "end": 63.0,
      "text": "몇 번 나왔어요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 63.28,
      "end": 66.3,
      "text": "You were on that show in 2019, right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 66.92,
      "end": 68.14,
      "text": "아마 그랬을 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 68.14,
      "end": 75.5,
      "text": "I was on maybe two or three times, 특집대, for a special episode, but I'm not a regular"
    },
    {
      "start": 75.5,
      "end": 76.22,
      "text": "on that show."
    },
    {
      "start": 76.52,
      "end": 77.32,
      "text": "그럼에도 불구하고."
    },
    {
      "start": 77.34,
      "end": 79.76,
      "text": "I'm surprised you remember me from that."
    },
    {
      "start": 79.92,
      "end": 81.42,
      "text": "와, 역시 G&P."
    },
    {
      "start": 81.86,
      "end": 83.48,
      "text": "와, 정말 감사합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 83.74,
      "end": 84.38,
      "text": "와, thank you."
    },
    {
      "start": 84.44,
      "end": 85.4,
      "text": "You make me feel special."
    },
    {
      "start": 85.64,
      "end": 86.24,
      "text": "그럼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 86.42,
      "end": 89.08,
      "text": "자, 오늘 이렇게 special하게 시작을 해볼 텐데."
    },
    {
      "start": 89.88,
      "end": 93.66,
      "text": "The movie is the story of a woman with two big problems."
    },
    {
      "start": 94.02,
      "end": 95.8,
      "text": "So, can you guess what they are?"
    },
    {
      "start": 95.8,
      "end": 101.86,
      "text": "So, one is her creative career is in, it's stalled."
    },
    {
      "start": 102.18,
      "end": 103.8,
      "text": "So, she's in a midlife crisis."
    },
    {
      "start": 103.94,
      "end": 104.08,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 104.22,
      "end": 105.84,
      "text": "And the other is mental illness."
    },
    {
      "start": 105.98,
      "end": 106.34,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 106.96,
      "end": 111.16,
      "text": "So, do you remember the jar with various and colorful pills?"
    },
    {
      "start": 111.8,
      "end": 112.74,
      "text": "All those pills?"
    },
    {
      "start": 112.86,
      "end": 113.18,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 113.44,
      "end": 113.78,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 113.78,
      "end": 119.08,
      "text": "All the colors of the rainbow are in the form of medicine pills in a big jar."
    },
    {
      "start": 119.16,
      "end": 119.58,
      "text": "그러니까요."
    },
    {
      "start": 119.58,
      "end": 120.58,
      "text": "All mixed together."
    },
    {
      "start": 120.84,
      "end": 126.42,
      "text": "만약 실제로 그런 거를 봤다면 가족의 입장에서는 걱정이 당연히 많이"
    },
    {
      "start": 126.42,
      "end": 127.34,
      "text": "됐을 거예요, 그죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 127.46,
      "end": 127.76,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 127.86,
      "end": 129.44,
      "text": "Oh, she's absolutely crazy."
    },
    {
      "start": 129.56,
      "end": 129.74,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 129.96,
      "end": 132.36,
      "text": "She doesn't even know what medication she's taking."
    },
    {
      "start": 132.82,
      "end": 134.98,
      "text": "But she never took it, fortunately."
    },
    {
      "start": 135.24,
      "end": 136.82,
      "text": "That is the good part."
    },
    {
      "start": 136.82,
      "end": 138.38,
      "text": "She just put all the pills in the jar."
    },
    {
      "start": 138.46,
      "end": 138.86,
      "text": "That's right."
    },
    {
      "start": 138.86,
      "end": 140.12,
      "text": "She's not taking any of them."
    },
    {
      "start": 140.62,
      "end": 145.88,
      "text": "아마 그녀가 그 약을 칵테일처럼 이렇게 섞어만 놓고 먹지 않은 이유가"
    },
    {
      "start": 145.88,
      "end": 146.94,
      "text": "따로 있었을 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 147.02,
      "end": 153.32,
      "text": "스스로 이유가 있다라는 것을 unconsciously, 무의식적으로 알고 있었기 때문이 아닐까"
    },
    {
      "start": 153.32,
      "end": 154.34,
      "text": "하는 생각도 해요."
    },
    {
      "start": 154.46,
      "end": 155.46,
      "text": "I think she knows, too."
    },
    {
      "start": 155.68,
      "end": 157.04,
      "text": "She knows the source of her troubles."
    },
    {
      "start": 157.24,
      "end": 157.36,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 157.36,
      "end": 162.74,
      "text": "She knows that she needs to create again, and these mental problems are getting worse"
    },
    {
      "start": 162.74,
      "end": 168.86,
      "text": "because she's not creating, she's not making beautiful homes as her role as an architect."
    },
    {
      "start": 169.7,
      "end": 174.56,
      "text": "And, you know, mental problems, sometimes they cannot be treated so well by medicine."
    },
    {
      "start": 174.76,
      "end": 176.52,
      "text": "You need a different outlet."
    },
    {
      "start": 176.76,
      "end": 178.84,
      "text": "You need a different source of treatment."
    },
    {
      "start": 178.84,
      "end": 179.2,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 180.02,
      "end": 189.34,
      "text": "약보다는 가끔은 정말 근본적인 원인을 파악을 해야 mental illness는 치료가 더 잘 되는 경우가 많죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 189.78,
      "end": 197.12,
      "text": "그래서 가족 간에 충분한 대화가 필요하고 또 관심이 아주 중요하구나라는 것을 다시 한번 상기시켜주는 영화입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 197.4,
      "end": 197.52,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 198.08,
      "end": 199.3,
      "text": "자, 오늘 내용 듣고 올게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 199.3,
      "end": 201.13,
      "text": "I don't know."
    },
    {
      "start": 201.97,
      "end": 203.43,
      "text": "How I'm going to make this up to you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 204.41,
      "end": 204.91,
      "text": "You're right."
    },
    {
      "start": 206.07,
      "end": 206.71,
      "text": "I need help."
    },
    {
      "start": 207.9,
      "end": 209.94,
      "text": "Let's start by spending time."
    },
    {
      "start": 210.02,
      "end": 210.86,
      "text": "We're together in Antarctica."
    },
    {
      "start": 211.54,
      "end": 213.06,
      "text": "You know, just the three of us."
    },
    {
      "start": 213.14,
      "end": 214.18,
      "text": "No work, no computers."
    },
    {
      "start": 214.42,
      "end": 217.66,
      "text": "Please, let's not blame this on Microsoft."
    },
    {
      "start": 218.06,
      "end": 220.52,
      "text": "No, I'm just saying the three of us."
    },
    {
      "start": 220.6,
      "end": 222.42,
      "text": "Her family, you know, without any distractions."
    },
    {
      "start": 222.84,
      "end": 227.06,
      "text": "The three of us are not going to Antarctica."
    },
    {
      "start": 228.35,
      "end": 232.63,
      "text": "어제의 장면에 이어서 오늘도 안타까움이 많이 느껴졌어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 232.99,
      "end": 235.99,
      "text": "She said she really wanted to go to Antarctica at this time."
    },
    {
      "start": 236.27,
      "end": 236.63,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 236.95,
      "end": 239.81,
      "text": "Before she was scared, she didn't want to go."
    },
    {
      "start": 239.81,
      "end": 240.43,
      "text": "그러니까요."
    },
    {
      "start": 240.43,
      "end": 242.71,
      "text": "But now she has a change of mind."
    },
    {
      "start": 242.81,
      "end": 243.05,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 243.49,
      "end": 247.93,
      "text": "이제 세 식구가 온전히 다녀오자라고 제안을 하는 장면이었습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 248.67,
      "end": 250.01,
      "text": "하지만 남편은 어땠죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 250.41,
      "end": 253.19,
      "text": "Oh, he wants to send her to an institution."
    },
    {
      "start": 253.45,
      "end": 253.99,
      "text": "Oh my God."
    },
    {
      "start": 253.99,
      "end": 255.17,
      "text": "요양 시술 같은데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 255.21,
      "end": 255.25,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 255.41,
      "end": 256.61,
      "text": "He's saying it was heartbreaking."
    },
    {
      "start": 257.05,
      "end": 257.45,
      "text": "Okay."
    },
    {
      "start": 257.75,
      "end": 258.39,
      "text": "Definitely."
    },
    {
      "start": 258.59,
      "end": 258.83,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 258.83,
      "end": 263.47,
      "text": "So she is furious and they have a 위기 왔어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 263.69,
      "end": 264.37,
      "text": "부부 위기."
    },
    {
      "start": 264.57,
      "end": 266.39,
      "text": "아주 심각한 위기였죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 266.85,
      "end": 268.59,
      "text": "표현들 먼저 점검을 해볼게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 268.59,
      "end": 272.06,
      "text": "How I'm going to make this up to you."
    },
    {
      "start": 272.06,
      "end": 280.68,
      "text": "이 문장에서 특별히 make up to somebody 라는 것을 좀 꼬집어서 이야기를 해드린다면"
    },
    {
      "start": 280.68,
      "end": 281.2,
      "text": "Make up."
    },
    {
      "start": 281.32,
      "end": 281.68,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 281.76,
      "end": 282.76,
      "text": "Make up이고 기본이에요."
    },
    {
      "start": 282.84,
      "end": 284.0,
      "text": "Let's make up 하면."
    },
    {
      "start": 284.0,
      "end": 284.52,
      "text": "보상하다."
    },
    {
      "start": 284.96,
      "end": 285.06,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 285.42,
      "end": 286.34,
      "text": "그리고 만회하다."
    },
    {
      "start": 286.64,
      "end": 287.12,
      "text": "화해하자."
    },
    {
      "start": 287.4,
      "end": 289.2,
      "text": "그 뜻으로도 많이 쓰여요."
    },
    {
      "start": 289.42,
      "end": 289.94,
      "text": "오키도키."
    },
    {
      "start": 290.04,
      "end": 290.6,
      "text": "우리 화해하자."
    },
    {
      "start": 290.74,
      "end": 291.62,
      "text": "Let's make up."
    },
    {
      "start": 291.78,
      "end": 292.52,
      "text": "화해하자."
    },
    {
      "start": 292.7,
      "end": 293.4,
      "text": "보상하자."
    },
    {
      "start": 293.54,
      "end": 294.26,
      "text": "만회하자."
    },
    {
      "start": 294.38,
      "end": 295.34,
      "text": "라는 의미라는 거죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 295.58,
      "end": 298.6,
      "text": "그래서 how I'm going to make this up to you 라고 했으니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 298.6,
      "end": 305.26,
      "text": "내가 어떻게 당신에게 이걸 보상할지 만회해야 할지 당신과 어떻게 화해해야 될지"
    },
    {
      "start": 305.26,
      "end": 307.0,
      "text": "이 정도로 해석하시면 돼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 307.18,
      "end": 309.04,
      "text": "항상 I don't know how."
    },
    {
      "start": 309.12,
      "end": 310.32,
      "text": "I don't know."
    },
    {
      "start": 310.68,
      "end": 311.48,
      "text": "앞에 나오겠죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 311.64,
      "end": 312.16,
      "text": "그렇겠죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 312.88,
      "end": 314.1,
      "text": "Let's not blame."
    },
    {
      "start": 314.1,
      "end": 317.3,
      "text": "아, blame이라는 게 비난하다, 탓하다 라는 거니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 317.3,
      "end": 322.64,
      "text": "Let's not blame 임으로 뭐 뭐 탓하지 말자 라고 해석하시면 되겠어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 322.78,
      "end": 324.0,
      "text": "Let's not blame anyone."
    },
    {
      "start": 324.4,
      "end": 326.02,
      "text": "Everybody is at fault."
    },
    {
      "start": 327.36,
      "end": 329.5,
      "text": "Without any distractions."
    },
    {
      "start": 329.9,
      "end": 335.24,
      "text": "네, distraction이라는 단어는 방해물, 방해라는 의미로 쓰이잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 335.26,
      "end": 341.16,
      "text": "그래서 without any distractions, 아무 방해 없이 라고 해석하시면 되겠어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 341.24,
      "end": 342.34,
      "text": "That's a great way to work."
    },
    {
      "start": 342.5,
      "end": 344.68,
      "text": "I want to work without any distractions."
    },
    {
      "start": 345.02,
      "end": 345.86,
      "text": "Don't bother me."
    },
    {
      "start": 346.12,
      "end": 348.26,
      "text": "자, 이 장면 한 번 더 들어보시죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 349.04,
      "end": 349.64,
      "text": "I don't know."
    },
    {
      "start": 350.48,
      "end": 351.94,
      "text": "How I'm going to make this up to you."
    },
    {
      "start": 352.93,
      "end": 353.41,
      "text": "You're right."
    },
    {
      "start": 354.57,
      "end": 355.21,
      "text": "I need help."
    },
    {
      "start": 356.4,
      "end": 359.42,
      "text": "Let's start by spending time together in Antarctica."
    },
    {
      "start": 360.06,
      "end": 361.56,
      "text": "You know, just the three of us."
    },
    {
      "start": 361.64,
      "end": 362.7,
      "text": "No work, no computers."
    },
    {
      "start": 362.7,
      "end": 365.7,
      "text": "Please, let's not blame this on Microsoft."
    },
    {
      "start": 366.06,
      "end": 369.02,
      "text": "No, I'm just saying the three of us."
    },
    {
      "start": 369.1,
      "end": 370.96,
      "text": "Her family, you know, without any distractions."
    },
    {
      "start": 371.36,
      "end": 375.56,
      "text": "The three of us are not going to Antarctica."
    },
    {
      "start": 376.77,
      "end": 379.97,
      "text": "오, LG의 반응은 was too firm."
    },
    {
      "start": 380.35,
      "end": 381.65,
      "text": "너무 확고하지 않습니까?"
    },
    {
      "start": 381.85,
      "end": 382.17,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 382.43,
      "end": 383.63,
      "text": "Well, he's made up his mind."
    },
    {
      "start": 383.77,
      "end": 384.07,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 384.15,
      "end": 385.87,
      "text": "You need help, mental help."
    },
    {
      "start": 386.03,
      "end": 387.33,
      "text": "We're not going anywhere."
    },
    {
      "start": 387.53,
      "end": 387.83,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 387.91,
      "end": 389.23,
      "text": "So he has set his mind."
    },
    {
      "start": 389.23,
      "end": 389.69,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 390.19,
      "end": 393.19,
      "text": "자, Bernadette이 먼저 뭐라고 이야기를 했는지 들어볼까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 393.99,
      "end": 396.83,
      "text": "I don't know how I'm going to make this up to you."
    },
    {
      "start": 396.91,
      "end": 397.33,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 397.69,
      "end": 402.37,
      "text": "아까 미리 그리스 씨가 이야기해 주신 것처럼 I don't know how, I don't know"
    },
    {
      "start": 402.37,
      "end": 405.71,
      "text": "가 앞에 있을 거다 라고 이야기해 주셨는데 딱 들렸죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 406.07,
      "end": 408.51,
      "text": "I don't know how I'm going to make this up to you."
    },
    {
      "start": 408.93,
      "end": 413.05,
      "text": "나는 이 일을 어떻게 만회해야 할지 모르겠어 라는 해석입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 413.05,
      "end": 414.71,
      "text": "So she does feel guilty."
    },
    {
      "start": 415.63,
      "end": 416.85,
      "text": "이제 좀 인정을 하나 봐요."
    },
    {
      "start": 417.09,
      "end": 423.43,
      "text": "She ruined her neighbor's house and she was talking to a criminal that she thought was"
    },
    {
      "start": 423.43,
      "end": 424.15,
      "text": "her secretary."
    },
    {
      "start": 424.17,
      "end": 424.37,
      "text": "That's true."
    },
    {
      "start": 425.09,
      "end": 426.19,
      "text": "She admits it."
    },
    {
      "start": 426.23,
      "end": 426.53,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 426.65,
      "end": 428.09,
      "text": "I don't know how I'm going to make this up to you."
    },
    {
      "start": 428.17,
      "end": 429.05,
      "text": "I'm so sorry."
    },
    {
      "start": 429.75,
      "end": 430.29,
      "text": "You're right."
    },
    {
      "start": 430.59,
      "end": 431.35,
      "text": "I need help."
    },
    {
      "start": 431.59,
      "end": 433.53,
      "text": "그러면서 다시 한 번 인정을 하죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 433.83,
      "end": 434.39,
      "text": "You're right."
    },
    {
      "start": 434.67,
      "end": 435.41,
      "text": "당신이 맞아."
    },
    {
      "start": 435.75,
      "end": 436.51,
      "text": "I need help."
    },
    {
      "start": 436.73,
      "end": 437.83,
      "text": "난 도움이 필요해."
    },
    {
      "start": 438.21,
      "end": 442.09,
      "text": "Let's start by spending time together in Antarctica."
    },
    {
      "start": 442.09,
      "end": 443.71,
      "text": "아, 도움이 필요해."
    },
    {
      "start": 443.79,
      "end": 447.65,
      "text": "그러니 나는 시설에 들어갈게 라고 이야기할 줄 알았는데 그 얘기가 아니라"
    },
    {
      "start": 447.65,
      "end": 448.33,
      "text": "No, no, no."
    },
    {
      "start": 448.95,
      "end": 453.03,
      "text": "Let's start by spending time together in Antarctica 라고 했어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 454.03,
      "end": 460.61,
      "text": "남극에서 우리가 함께 시간을 보냄으로써 한번 시작을 해보자 라고 제안을 하고 있어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 460.85,
      "end": 462.91,
      "text": "You know, just the three of us."
    },
    {
      "start": 463.69,
      "end": 468.05,
      "text": "당신 우리 세 명만 딱 말이야 라고 이야기하는 거죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 468.17,
      "end": 469.71,
      "text": "No work, no computers."
    },
    {
      "start": 469.71,
      "end": 473.55,
      "text": "어떤 일도 없이, 어떠한 컴퓨터도 없이"
    },
    {
      "start": 473.55,
      "end": 475.53,
      "text": "Please, please."
    },
    {
      "start": 476.03,
      "end": 478.63,
      "text": "Let's not blame this on Microsoft."
    },
    {
      "start": 479.35,
      "end": 480.69,
      "text": "남편이 하는 말이었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 481.23,
      "end": 484.01,
      "text": "Please, let's not blame this on Microsoft."
    },
    {
      "start": 485.43,
      "end": 488.15,
      "text": "Microsoft의 이 일을 탓하지 말자 라는 거니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 488.15,
      "end": 491.53,
      "text": "아, 제발 내 회사 탓은 하지 말자 라는 거죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 491.69,
      "end": 492.83,
      "text": "Oh, he's getting sensitive."
    },
    {
      "start": 493.11,
      "end": 493.33,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 493.57,
      "end": 495.23,
      "text": "This is not because of my work."
    },
    {
      "start": 495.37,
      "end": 496.55,
      "text": "This is your problem."
    },
    {
      "start": 496.55,
      "end": 498.87,
      "text": "He was strongly devoted to his company."
    },
    {
      "start": 499.29,
      "end": 501.19,
      "text": "Yeah, remember, he worked all the time."
    },
    {
      "start": 501.27,
      "end": 501.45,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 501.67,
      "end": 502.27,
      "text": "Alcoholic."
    },
    {
      "start": 502.43,
      "end": 503.15,
      "text": "Not alcoholic."
    },
    {
      "start": 503.81,
      "end": 504.07,
      "text": "Sorry."
    },
    {
      "start": 504.19,
      "end": 504.71,
      "text": "Workaholic."
    },
    {
      "start": 504.99,
      "end": 505.81,
      "text": "술은 안 먹었고."
    },
    {
      "start": 505.85,
      "end": 506.05,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 506.25,
      "end": 506.89,
      "text": "Workaholic."
    },
    {
      "start": 506.97,
      "end": 507.15,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 507.35,
      "end": 509.29,
      "text": "애사심이 아주 대단한 사람입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 510.51,
      "end": 510.81,
      "text": "No."
    },
    {
      "start": 511.31,
      "end": 513.11,
      "text": "I'm just saying the three of us."
    },
    {
      "start": 513.43,
      "end": 517.51,
      "text": "아니, 나는 우리 딱 셋이서만을 이야기하는 거야."
    },
    {
      "start": 518.01,
      "end": 520.71,
      "text": "Our family without any distractions."
    },
    {
      "start": 520.71,
      "end": 524.45,
      "text": "우리 가족만 아무런 방해도 없이 말이야."
    },
    {
      "start": 524.97,
      "end": 526.07,
      "text": "Ah, yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 526.19,
      "end": 526.79,
      "text": "Family time."
    },
    {
      "start": 526.97,
      "end": 528.65,
      "text": "Work is good without distractions."
    },
    {
      "start": 528.87,
      "end": 529.01,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 529.17,
      "end": 530.23,
      "text": "Also, family time."
    },
    {
      "start": 530.31,
      "end": 532.47,
      "text": "It's best without any distractions."
    },
    {
      "start": 532.85,
      "end": 533.69,
      "text": "Necessary 하죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 534.49,
      "end": 537.47,
      "text": "The three of us are not going to Antarctica."
    },
    {
      "start": 537.73,
      "end": 540.79,
      "text": "네, 하지만 남편은 이렇게 단호하게 이야기를 합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 540.99,
      "end": 544.15,
      "text": "The three of us are not going to Antarctica."
    },
    {
      "start": 544.15,
      "end": 545.07,
      "text": "라고 했으니까."
    },
    {
      "start": 545.51,
      "end": 549.37,
      "text": "우리 셋이 남극에 가는 일은 없을 거야."
    },
    {
      "start": 549.73,
      "end": 550.41,
      "text": "라는 이야기예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 550.45,
      "end": 551.77,
      "text": "Oh, he's putting his foot down."
    },
    {
      "start": 551.85,
      "end": 552.05,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 552.15,
      "end": 553.13,
      "text": "No, I'm saying no."
    },
    {
      "start": 553.33,
      "end": 554.07,
      "text": "No more."
    },
    {
      "start": 554.17,
      "end": 555.53,
      "text": "It's not going to happen."
    },
    {
      "start": 555.61,
      "end": 555.99,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 556.13,
      "end": 556.87,
      "text": "On my watch."
    },
    {
      "start": 556.97,
      "end": 559.39,
      "text": "아하, 더 이상 이 얘기하지 마."
    },
    {
      "start": 559.63,
      "end": 562.87,
      "text": "나는 당신과 우리 셋이서 남극에 절대 가지 않을 거야."
    },
    {
      "start": 562.99,
      "end": 563.39,
      "text": "이제 끝!"
    },
    {
      "start": 563.77,
      "end": 565.19,
      "text": "이런 뉘앙스가 들렸어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 565.19,
      "end": 566.87,
      "text": "Oh, 어떻게 해야 되나?"
    },
    {
      "start": 567.11,
      "end": 570.47,
      "text": "네, 그러면 이제 남편이 약간 버네덴만 제외시키고"
    },
    {
      "start": 570.47,
      "end": 573.45,
      "text": "He's going to take a trip to Antarctica with his daughter B."
    },
    {
      "start": 573.45,
      "end": 575.03,
      "text": "Oh, is that his plan?"
    },
    {
      "start": 575.11,
      "end": 575.39,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 575.67,
      "end": 577.87,
      "text": "Oh, because B, he doesn't want to disappoint B."
    },
    {
      "start": 577.95,
      "end": 579.61,
      "text": "B는 정말 가고 싶어 하니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 579.61,
      "end": 581.21,
      "text": "내가 딸이랑 같이 갔다 올 테니"
    },
    {
      "start": 581.21,
      "end": 582.81,
      "text": "당신은 요양시설에 들어가 있어."
    },
    {
      "start": 582.93,
      "end": 583.65,
      "text": "라는 이야기였어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 583.67,
      "end": 584.39,
      "text": "더 기분 아프겠어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 584.41,
      "end": 584.71,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 585.29,
      "end": 586.69,
      "text": "아, 정말."
    },
    {
      "start": 587.09,
      "end": 590.13,
      "text": "화가 났지만 한 번 더 점검해 볼게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 591.93,
      "end": 594.85,
      "text": "I don't know how I'm going to make this up to you."
    },
    {
      "start": 595.82,
      "end": 596.32,
      "text": "You're right."
    },
    {
      "start": 597.46,
      "end": 598.1,
      "text": "I need help."
    },
    {
      "start": 599.29,
      "end": 602.33,
      "text": "Let's start by spending time together in Antarctica."
    },
    {
      "start": 602.33,
      "end": 604.47,
      "text": "You know, just the three of us."
    },
    {
      "start": 604.47,
      "end": 605.59,
      "text": "no work, no computers."
    },
    {
      "start": 605.81,
      "end": 609.05,
      "text": "Please, let's not blame this on Microsoft."
    },
    {
      "start": 609.47,
      "end": 611.91,
      "text": "No, I'm just saying the three of us."
    },
    {
      "start": 612.01,
      "end": 613.83,
      "text": "Her family, you know, without any distractions."
    },
    {
      "start": 614.25,
      "end": 618.47,
      "text": "The three of us are not going to Antarctica."
    },
    {
      "start": 618.47,
      "end": 625.16,
      "text": "네, 과연 정말 Bernadette is going to get locked up at the 치료소?"
    },
    {
      "start": 625.28,
      "end": 626.28,
      "text": "A mental institution?"
    },
    {
      "start": 626.28,
      "end": 630.64,
      "text": "Oh, 진짜 과연 그럴지 벌써부터 궁금해지는데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 631.0,
      "end": 633.5,
      "text": "Yeah, I think she'll not like that."
    },
    {
      "start": 633.66,
      "end": 636.3,
      "text": "She'd rather run far away than have that happen."
    },
    {
      "start": 636.5,
      "end": 637.24,
      "text": "아, 예."
    },
    {
      "start": 637.32,
      "end": 638.48,
      "text": "스포는 여기까지."
    },
    {
      "start": 639.18,
      "end": 639.88,
      "text": "Where'd you go?"
    },
    {
      "start": 640.02,
      "end": 641.24,
      "text": "아, 그래서 where'd you go인가?"
    },
    {
      "start": 641.42,
      "end": 642.5,
      "text": "그럴 수도 있겠네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 642.86,
      "end": 644.82,
      "text": "네, 우리 여기에 더 마무리하고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 644.9,
      "end": 645.8,
      "text": "내일 다시 만날게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 645.8,
      "end": 646.46,
      "text": "See you tomorrow."
    }
  ]
}